title: Pitt
description:
Pitt is a human/alien hybrid, created by an alien race known as the Creed, genetically engineered to serve as a killing machine. Pitt escapes his home world and makes his way to Earth. But, is it fate or something else that draws him to rescue Timmy Bracken and his grampa when thugs storm a New York subway-car?

Created and illustrated by Dale Keown.


Released on http://ComicPirates.info
